{"success":true,"result":{"Q_10106712693591-2":{"resources":[],"questions":[{"id":"Q_10106712693591-2","subjectId":101,"knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":[],"testMethods":[{"id":"TM_10100000672366","main":1}],"solutionMethods":[],"resourceIds":null,"resourceIndex":0,"listenUrl":null,"listenName":null,"listenSeconds":0,"exploreSeconds":0,"answersSeconds":0,"paperIds":["P_10100076786734-2"],"books":null,"booksNew":null,"contentTypeId":1010008,"contentType2Id":0,"difficultyInt":3,"description":"阅读文章，回答问题","notFitMobile":0,"seconds":480,"complex":1,"nid":null,"lastEditorId":null,"finalAuditorId":null,"roughAuditorIds":null,"content":{"content":"<p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">一天晚上，刘琨登上城楼巡察。这时，城里城外一片寂静，一轮明月挂在空中，月光下，远处匈奴骑兵的营地隐约可见。刘琨凝视远方，面对边塞的冷月、荒漠、山丘、孤城······禁不住发出一声声长啸。那一声声凄厉的长啸，在夜深人静时传得很远，传到匈奴的兵营，把匈奴兵惊醒了。匈奴兵营里发出一阵骚动。</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">这一下启发了刘琨，他想起了当年项羽的八千兵马被“四面楚歌”唱败的故事，想出了一个计谋。刘琨忙叫人取来匈奴人最喜爱的乐器——胡笳，朝匈奴兵营吹奏起来。胡笳曲是那么悦耳动听，又是那么哀伤凄婉，就像是年老的慈母在呼唤久别的孩子，又像是年轻的妻子在思念在外的丈夫······</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">刘琨一遍遍地吹奏着那深情的乐曲，连自己也被感动得流下了热泪。这时，忽然有人发现匈奴兵营有了动静，传来幽幽的哭泣声。</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">“将军，那边有人在哭。”卫兵报告刘琨。“注意动静，严密防守。”刘琨及时作了布置，然后回营房和众将商量对策。第二天一早，卫兵赶来报告，说匈奴兵已经全部撤走了。刘琨听了，好似卸下了千斤重担。</p>","contentDesc":"","analysis":"","subContents":[{"content":"<p>从文中找出下面词语的近义词。</p><p>注视——__$$__</p>","answers":[{"answer":"凝视","subAnswers":["凝视"],"richTexts":null,"scorePercentage":1,"classification":"","knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":[{"id":"KP_10100078259008","tagId":0,"main":1,"featureIds":[]}],"testMethods":[{"id":"TM_10100000631040","main":1}],"solutionMethods":[],"classificationListenUrl":null}],"subContentTypeId":4,"analysis":"","optionType":"word","options":[],"hideOptionNumber":0,"listenUrl":"","listenName":"","listenSeconds":0,"exploreSeconds":0,"answersSeconds":0,"oralDict":{"seconds":null,"variables":null,"keywords":null,"options":null,"voiceText":null,"sentencePatterns":null,"picUrl":null,"picName":null,"beginListenUrl":null,"endListenUrl":nu